Compile:

to compile the RedCap Client you just have to run the Makefile with Make
if you are under MacOSX you will have to comment and uncomment 2 lignes
if you are using NetBSD there is also one line to comment and uncomment in includes/includes.h


Use:

launch ./Redcap then open a telnet connection on localhost on port 5505

then for the momment there is only a few command that are implemented:

connect login[:password]@host[:port] (auto_agree)
:to connect to an hotline server

send_chat "my message"
:to send chat in public chat

get_user_list
:to obtain user list on the server

get_file_list
:to obtain file list on the server

next_server
:go to next server

previous_server
:go to previous server

list_server
:list all connected server